name: N!GHTMARES by MAG!C #8
description: N!GHTMARES is a collection of digital works by AI artist MAG!C.  These pieces were created as a reminder that even when our eyes are open, the trauma from our nightmares and past experiences continue to haunt us through our day.  MAG!C combats his trauma by embracing darkness through art, as a healthy and often healing form of expression.  MAG!C is an up and coming artist that is gaining a lot of traction in the NFT world, so jump on these before the rest of the world catches on!
